text.tspan: Death rate in state-based conflicts, World
Deaths of combatants and civilians due to fighting, per 100,000 people. Included are interstate, intrastate, and
extrasystemic conflicts that were ongoing that year.
Data source: Uppsala Conflict Data Program (2024); Peace Research Institute Oslo (2017); Population based on various sources (2024)
